RendererType
public class RendererTypeImpl
extends EObjectImpl
implements RendererType

An implementation of the model object 'Renderer Type'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Description
  • Display Name
  • Icon
  • Component Family
  • Renderer Type
  • Renderer Class
  • Facet
  • Attribute
  • Renderer Extension
  • Id
